public String thousandSeparator(int n) {
    String result = Integer.toString(n);
    int count = 0;
    for (int i = result.length() - 1; i > 0; --i) {
        count++;
        if (count % 3 == 0) {
            result = result.substring(0, i) + "." + result.substring(i);
        }
    }
    return result;
}
```

